➡️ Cell 1 — Install dependency
!pip install -q streamlit google-generativeai cloudflared

➡️ Cell 2 — Masukkan API Key (otomatis membuat secrets.toml)
import os

API_KEY = "ISI_API_KEY_MU_DISINI"  # ganti dengan API Key kamu

os.makedirs("/root/.streamlit", exist_ok=True)

with open("/root/.streamlit/secrets.toml", "w") as f:
    f.write(f"GEMINI_API_KEY = '{API_KEY}'")

print("API key saved successfully!")

➡️ Cell 3 — Clone repository GitHub kamu

(Ganti USERNAME dan repo name nanti setelah kamu upload)

!rm -rf project-gemini-chatbot
!git clone https://github.com/USERNAME/project-gemini-chatbot.git
%cd project-gemini-chatbot

➡️ Cell 4 — Jalankan Streamlit
!streamlit run app.py &>/content/logs.txt &

➡️ Cell 5 — Buat URL publik via Cloudflare Tunnel
!cloudflared tunnel --url http://localhost:8501 --no-autoupdate


Setelah itu akan muncul link seperti:

https://happy-sunset-blue.trycloudflare.com


Tinggal klik → aplikasi langsung terbuka.
